		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Cool, I always through it could be interesting to run faster than 50/60 Hz. Many SNES games do stuff like that in their sound effects - it's the "standard" of the console because a 1,02 Mhz CPU is dedicated entirely to sound. This isn't the case on the NES.

		

