<br />
<br />I used some commercial music drivers to make some basic scales played simutaneously on each of the channels, but nothing more complex than that. But of course I really can't use them for games or music competitions. (I doubt it anyways). If you don't mind, I have some questions about Nijuu to ask you. I won't here because that's off topic. I'd like to send you a private message if you don't mind.

		

