	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe plain cycle timing? If you do it all from an NMI handler, you'd cycle time the first three 1/240 periods, then return from the handler after the fourth update for that frame, leaving about 1/240 second free to the non-NMI code.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


